from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "pellets" and
    r._field == "count" and
    r.run =~ /^${run:regex}$/ and
    r.scenario =~ /^${scenario:regex}$/
  )

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "pellets" and
    r._field == "energy" and
    r.run =~ /^${run:regex}$/ and
    r.scenario =~ /^${scenario:regex}$/
  )

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "census" and
    r._field == "count" and
    r.species == "${species}" and
    r.run =~ /^${run:regex}$/ and
    r.scenario =~ /^${scenario:regex}$/
  )
  |> group(columns: ["scenario"])

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "census" and
    r._field == "Diet_mean" and
    r.species == "${species}" and
    r.run =~ /^${run:regex}$/ and
    r.scenario =~ /^${scenario:regex}$/
  )
  |> group(columns: ["scenario"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1m, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)

list.definition:
import "influxdata/influxdb/v1"
v1.tagValues(
    bucket: v.bucket,
    tag: "run",
    predicate: (r) => true,
    start: -1d
)
